message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - This paper deals with deep learning-based medical image segmentation, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) domains. The use of uncertainty estimates is a recent development in the machine learning community (cs.AI), and the application of these techniques to medical imaging is a growing area of research (cs.MED). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of neural networks (cs.NEURON) for segmentation tasks.
